OL,3,CRTE funding model cannot be 'sticking
OL,4,Cplaster solution' ` Simon Harris
OL,6,FThe future funding model of RTE must
OL,7,Fnot be a "sticking plaster solution",
OL,8,Fthe Taoiseach has said.
OL,10,FSimon Harris made the remarks as RTE
OL,11,Fwaits for a decision on the model
OL,12,Fafter the broadcaster published a road
OL,13,Fmap for reform.
OL,15,FAsked for his opinion on the RTE
OL,16,Freform plan, Mr Harris said: "I think
OL,17,Fit's a very good start. I think that's
OL,18,Fwhat it is ` a very good start.
