OL,3,CRTE funding model cannot be 'sticking
OL,4,Cplaster solution' ` Simon Harris
OL,6,F"I do accept that the ball is now back
OL,7,Fin our court and I do think, in
OL,8,Ffairness to RTE and what RTE staff
OL,9,Fhave gone through over the last period
OL,10,Fand the stressful period of time, I do
OL,11,Fthink the ball is now back in our
OL,12,Fcourt in terms of making a decision on
OL,13,Fa funding model for public service
OL,14,Fbroadcasting."
OL,16,FMr Harris said the decision should be
OL,17,Fmade by the end of July.
OL,19,FSpeaking to reporters at the Night And
OL,20,FDay festival, Mr Harris added: "Any
OL,21,Fthing we do needs to be sustainable.
