OL,3,CRTE funding model cannot be 'sticking
OL,4,Cplaster solution' ` Simon Harris
OL,6,F"There's no point doing something that
OL,7,Fmakes public service broadcasting
OL,8,Fsustainable for a few years but find
OL,9,Fout we're back where we began.
OL,11,F"Like we have to factor in things like
OL,12,Fdemographics. For example, we have an
OL,13,Fageing population.
OL,15,F"Quite rightly, people of a certain
OL,16,Fage aren't asked to pay the licence
OL,17,Ffee. I support that. That will
OL,18,Fobviously have to continue if the
OL,19,Flicence fee remains.
