OL,3,CRTE funding model cannot be 'sticking
OL,4,Cplaster solution' ` Simon Harris
OL,6,F"But that needs to be factored in as
OL,7,Fthat demographic bulge may grow into
OL,8,Fthe future.
OL,10,F"There can't be a sticking plaster
OL,11,Fsolution, there has to be a
OL,12,Fsustainable model."
OL,14,FHe added: "We need to fix this for
OL,15,Fpublic service broadcasting ` not just
OL,16,Ffor RTE but it also has to be linked
OL,17,Fto continued ongoing reform in RTE."
